name: 🚗🚗🚗 A Car Crash #NFT 🚗🚗🚗
description: Question: “If a car crashes in the forest but there’s nobody around to hear it, does it make a sound?” No, it makes a riot of colors 🌈 instead.  This is another one from my magical forest series.  Made with my trusty digital camera and a heavy sprinkling of Photoshop.  Tweet me @fotokopid
